<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Write-up: [LAB NAME]</title>
    <style>
        /* Core Terminal Colors */
        :root {
            --terminal-green: #39FF14;
            --dim-green: #32CD32;
            --bg-black: #000000;
            --code-bg: #1a1a1a;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-black);
            color: var(--terminal-green);
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0; /* Handled by container */
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        .post-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px; /* Essential padding for mobile edges */
        }

        /* Responsive Header */
        h1 { 
            font-size: 1.8rem; 
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--terminal-green); 
            padding-bottom: 10px; 
            text-transform: uppercase;
            word-wrap: break-word; /* Prevents long titles from breaking mobile layout */
        }

        .breadcrumb { font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 15px; opacity: 0.7; }
        .breadcrumb a { color: var(--terminal-green); text-decoration: none; }
        
        .metadata { 
            font-size: 0.75rem; 
            margin-bottom: 25px; 
            color: #888;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        /* Content Sections */
        h2 { 
            font-size: 1.2rem; 
            color: #fff; 
            background: #111; 
            padding: 8px 12px; 
            display: block; 
            margin-top: 35px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--terminal-green);
        }

        p { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }
        
        /* Mobile-Friendly Code Blocks */
        pre { 
            background: var(--code-bg); 
            padding: 15px; 
            border-radius: 4px;
            overflow-x: auto; /* Allows side-scrolling for long commands on mobile */
            white-space: pre-wrap; /* Wraps text if it's too long */
            word-break: break-all;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #333;
        }

        /* Phenomenal Image Handling */
        .screenshot-box {
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .screenshot-box img {
            width: 100%; /* Scales to screen width */
            height: auto;
            border: 1px solid var(--terminal-green);
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: block;
        }
        .caption { 
            font-size: 0.8rem; 
            margin-top: 10px; 
            color: var(--dim-green); 
            font-style: italic; 
        }

        /* Navigation */
        .footer-nav { 
            margin-top: 50px; 
            border-top: 1px solid #333; 
            padding: 20px 0; 
        }
        .back-btn { 
            color: var(--terminal-green); 
            text-decoration: none; 
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        /* MOBILE OPTIMIZATIONS (The "Phenomenal" part) */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .post-container { padding: 15px; }
            h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
            h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; }
            p { font-size: 1rem; }
            pre { font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 10px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="post-container">
        <div class="breadcrumb">
            <a href="../index.html">root</a> / <a href="../oscp.html">oscp_log</a> / write-up
        </div>

        <header>
            <h1>[Lab Name: Target Machine]</h1>
            <div class="metadata">
                <span>DATE: 2026-05-12</span>
                <span>|</span>
                <span>CAT: PEN-TESTING</span>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section>
            <h2>01. Executive Summary</h2>
            <p>Briefly describe the objective. High-level, clear, and direct.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>02. Tactical Execution</h2>
            <p>Paste your terminal commands below. On mobile, these will wrap so you don't have to scroll horizontally to read them.</p>
            <pre># Example: Running an aggressive Nmap scan
nmap -A -T4 -p- 10.10.10.x</pre>
        </section>

        <!-- IMAGE SLOT 1 -->
        <div class="screenshot-box">
            <img src="../images/placeholder.png" alt="Screenshot of terminal output">
            <div class="caption">Fig 1: Identifying open ports and service versions.</div>
        </div>

        <section>
            <h2>03. Critical Findings</h2>
            <p>This is where you explain the "Why." What did you see in **Wireshark** or **Nmap** that gave you the next clue?</p>
        </section>

        <!-- IMAGE SLOT 2 -->
        <div class="screenshot-box">
            <img src="../images/placeholder2.png" alt="Screenshot of exploit code">
            <div class="caption">Fig 2: Analyzing the response headers for version vulnerabilities.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-nav">
            <a href="../oscp.html" class="back-btn"><-- LOG_LIST</a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
